#

Baked Tofu with Vegetables

45 min
$8
350 kcal
Difficulty: 20%
Servings: 2

Allergens:

Soy

Dietary Tags:

VegetarianVeganGluten-Free

Cuisine:

Asian

Course:

Main Dish

Tags:

EasyHealthyComfort Food

Description

A simple, flavorful dish packed with nutritious vegetables and protein-rich tofu, baked to perfection.

Ingredients

  • firm tofu: 14 oz
  • bell pepper: 1
  • zucchini: 1
  • carrot: 1
  • olive oil: 2 tbsp
  • soy sauce: 2 tbsp
  • garlic powder: 1 tsp
  • salt: to taste
  • black pepper: to taste
  • sesame seeds: 1 tbsp (optional)
